    <item>
      <title>米其林挑战欧盟寻找轮胎卡特尔证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着监管机构席卷整个轮胎行业，寻找涉嫌垄断价格卡特尔的证据，米其林正在挑战欧盟对其设施进行反垄断搜查的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员提出禁止算法稳定币的新法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/senators-tout-new-stablecoin-bill-as-broader-banking-deal-eyed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位参议员——一名共和党人，一名民主党人——在众议院和参议院推动最快下个月通过此类立法的过程中，正在提出一项监管稳定币的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/senators-tout-new-stablecoin-bill-as-broader-banking-deal-eyed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求对中国钢铁和铝征收更高关税以支持美国企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/higher-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-aluminum-sought-by-biden-in-2024-election-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登呼吁对中国钢铁和铝征收更高的关税，这是支撑美国钢铁行业并在今年大选中吸引工人的一系列措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/higher-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-aluminum-sought-by-biden-in-2024-election-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
